title: Fetty Wap Get's 5 Years For Role In Drug Ring
itunes:title: Fetty Wap Get's 5 Years For Role In Drug Ring
description:
Multi platinum artist Fetty Wap was recently sentenced to 5 years for his role in a nationwide drug ring involving coke, heroin and fentanyl and ask after all his success, what led him to hustling?
